### GET Employees
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

### GET with expand
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Employees?$expand=banks,educations,experiences,documents,statutoryDetails

### POST Employee
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ID": "2647f862-950c-48a6-b490-6e65dbf04285",
    "mobile":"9985251944"
}

### GET Banks
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Banks

### Create bank account
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Banks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employee_ID":"2647f862-950c-48a6-b490-6e65dbf04285",
    "bankName":"ICICI Bank",
    "branchName":"Hyderabad",
    "accountHolderName":"Rahul Sharma",
    "accountNumber":"123456789012",
    "accountType":"Salary",
    "currency":"INR",
    "ifscCode":"ICIC0001234",
    "swiftCode":"ICICINBB",
    "upiId":"rahul@icici"
}

### Create bank account
PUT http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/employee/Banks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employee_ID":"2647f862-950c-48a6-b490-6e65dbf04285",
